        <item>
        <title>Compinit 503 No Such File or Directory in Zinit</title>
        <link>/posts/archives/linux/compinit-503-no-such-file-or-directory-in-zinit/</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 20 Oct 2021 14:59:00 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>/posts/archives/linux/compinit-503-no-such-file-or-directory-in-zinit/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;在使用zinit安装插件时反复调试时可能出现&lt;code&gt;compinit:503: no such file or directory: ~/.zinit/completions/_xxx&lt;/code&gt;问题，但是并不影响正常使用，只是在首次进入后提示两次&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;解决&#34;&gt;解决
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;运行&lt;code&gt;zinit cclear&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
